            "faq_1_question": "When is the Mid-Year Surprise Drop available?",
            "faq_1_answer": "The Mid-Year Surprise Drop is available from April 29 to May 20. Event offers, new arrivals, daily gift card surprises, and eligible coupons are valid during this period only.",
